Install the 64-bit version of the Microsoft Online Services Sign-in Assistant: Microsoft Online Services 
Sign-in Assistant for IT Professionals RTW.
https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=286152

Install the Microsoft Azure Active Directory Module for Windows PowerShell with these steps:

Open an elevated Windows PowerShell command prompt (run Windows PowerShell as an administrator).
Run the Install-Module MSOnline command.
If prompted to install the NuGet provider, type Y and press ENTER.
If prompted to install the module from PSGallery, type Y and press ENTER.
Maybe a new way? (Install-Module -Name MSOnline)

Connect- MSolService


